"The `string methods "
"<https://docs.python.org/en/3/library/stdtypes.html#string-methods>`__ are "
"functions that work on strings, which are used as argument."
#: ../../source/python-textos-metodos.rst:16
msgid ""
"Al estar asociadas a las cadenas de texto, se las llama añadiendo un punto y"
